Status: ☑

--- Acceptance Criteria ---
AC1: MetricsHandler 使用 promhttp.Handler() 输出 Go runtime + process 指标
AC2: /metrics 输出含 go_gc_duration_seconds
AC3: /metrics 输出含 process_cpu_seconds_total
AC4: 自定义 md_* 指标保持不变
AC5: go build ./... pass
AC6: go vet ./... pass
AC7: go test ./internal/mdgateway/... pass

--- Step 1: 当前状态 ---
Before: MetricsHandler() 手写 text/plain HTTP handler，在 bytes.Buffer 里自己拼 Prometheus 格式。
        无 Go runtime 指标，无 process 指标，无 HTTP 请求统计，无 DB 连接池指标。
After:  MetricsHandler() 内部分为两步:
       1. writeLegacyMetrics → 写自定义 md_* 指标
       2. promhttp.Handler() → 写 Go runtime + process + 默认 registry 指标

--- Step 2: 实现 ---
新增辅助类型和函数:

type captureWriter struct {
    headers http.Header
    buf     *bytes.Buffer
}
func (w *captureWriter) Header() http.Header         { return w.headers }
func (w *captureWriter) Write(b []byte) (int, error) { return w.buf.Write(b) }
func (w *captureWriter) WriteHeader(statusCode int)   {}

func writeLegacyMetrics(b *strings.Builder) {
    // ...所有原有 md_* 指标不变
}

func MetricsHandler() http.Handler {
    return http.HandlerFunc(func(w http.ResponseWriter, r *http.Request) {
        w.Header().Set("Content-Type", "text/plain; version=0.0.4")
        var b strings.Builder
        writeLegacyMetrics(&b)
        var buf bytes.Buffer
        cw := &captureWriter{headers: make(http.Header), buf: &buf}
        promhttp.Handler().ServeHTTP(cw, r)
        b.Write(buf.Bytes())
        w.Write([]byte(b.String()))
    })
}

关键设计:
- captureWriter 实现 http.ResponseWriter 接口，捕获 promhttp 输出到 buffer
- promhttp.Handler() 使用默认 prometheus.DefaultGatherer，自动包含:
  - GoCollector: go_gc_duration_seconds, go_goroutines, go_memstats_*, etc.
  - ProcessCollector: process_cpu_seconds_total, process_resident_memory_bytes, etc.
- 两个源的输出合并写入同一个响应体

